workarounds so far 

1. commented 
"before_filter :redirect_to_https, :only => :index"
to make it work without https on local setup

2. activating users as cant send mail for verification 

a. go to 
http://0.0.0.0:3001/password_resets/new
b. enter email of user you want to activate 
e.g viewer@foo.com
c. 
$ sudo -u postgres psql
postgres=# \connect user_service_development_1
postgres=# select * from users;

