 d . copy password_reset_token 
 e . use this => "http://user-owner.herokuapp.com/en/password_resets/AOBp8JGFtBISIY8VWydbCw/edit" URL and replace it with "http://YOUR_SERVER_HERE/en/password_resets/PASSWORD_RESET_TOKEN_COPIED/edit"
 F. Use above custom url to reset the password and then user is activted